vulnerability_report.title: CRITICAL: Prototype Pollution Leading to Privilege Escalation
vulnerability_report.cwe: CWE-1321: Improperly Controlled Modification of Object Prototype

executive_summary.description: Kritična Prototype Pollution ranjivost je identifikovana koja omogućava napadaču da manipuliše JavaScript Object prototype, što može rezultovati u privilege escalation, authorization bypass, i u najgorim slučajevima Remote Code Execution.

technical_details.root_cause: Insufficient input validation na JSON objektima koji omogućava manipulaciju __proto__ property
technical_details.attack_vector: HTTP POST requests sa malicious JSON payloadi
